    neutron scattering data, general atomic report ga-8774          58 1451     
    revised and reissued as endf-269 by the national nuclear        58 1451     
    data center, july 1978.                                         58 1451     
 2. e.l.slaggie, "central force lattice dynamical model for         58 1451     
    zirconium hydride", ga-8132 (1967).                             58 1451     
 3. r.e.macfarlane, new thermal neutron scattering files for        58 1451     
    endf/b-vi release 2, los alamos national laboratory report      58 1451     
    LA-12639-MS (ENDF-356) March 1994.                              58 1451     
